{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "ac5ea9e3-f509-47d0-86af-d3bdad2649f6", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ac5ea9e3-f509-47d0-86af-d3bdad2649f6@1.pkg/1772597575297/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597575509", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ac5ea9e3-f509-47d0-86af-d3bdad2649f6@1.pkg/1772597575297/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597575509"}, "identifier": "ac5ea9e3-f509-47d0-86af-d3bdad2649f6", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查对 &ldquo;回望成长&rdquo; 中初中三年成长意义的理解。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A：小李在初中三年中，从性格突破到学习进步，再到参与集体和社会活动，体现了初中阶段在探索中不断成长，能力与责任感逐步提升，符合 &ldquo;回望成长&rdquo; 中成长是积累经验、提升自我的过程这一知识点，故 A 符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B：&ldquo;只要专注学习，就能实现所有目标&rdquo; 说法绝对，成长需要兼顾学习与实践、个人与集体等多方面，并非仅靠专注学习就能达成所有目标；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C：&ldquo;把集体活动放在首位，忽视个人发展&rdquo; 错误，个人发展与集体活动相辅相成，不应忽视任何一方；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D：&ldquo;性格和能力的改变主要依靠他人帮助&rdquo; 错误，成长的根本动力源于自身努力，他人帮助是外部条件，而非主要依靠；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>故本题选 A。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（原创）</span><span>小李在初中毕业总结中写道：三年来，我从起初的腼腆内向，到主动参与班级管理；从数学成绩垫底，到通过错题整理、请教老师逆袭成学科代表；还和同学组建环保小组，在社区开展垃圾分类宣传。这段经历说明初中三年，我们（ ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）小李在初中毕业总结中写道：三年来，我从起初的腼腆内向，到主动参与班级管理；从数学成绩垫底，到通过错题整理、请教老师逆袭成学科代表；还和同学组建环保小组，在社区开展垃圾分类宣传。这段经历说明初中三年，我们（ ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ac5ea9e3-f509-47d0-86af-d3bdad2649f6@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984729136", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>在探索中成长，逐渐提升能力与责任感</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>只要专注学习，就能实现所有目标</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>应把集体活动放在首位，忽视个人发展</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>性格和能力的改变主要依靠他人帮助</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（原创）</span><span>小李在初中毕业总结中写道：三年来，我从起初的腼腆内向，到主动参与班级管理；从数学成绩垫底，到通过错题整理、请教老师逆袭成学科代表；还和同学组建环保小组，在社区开展垃圾分类宣传。这段经历说明初中三年，我们（ ）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blank